 <item rdf:about="https://maritime-union.com/job/223017/">
  <description>&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Europe&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;font-family:Arial,sans-serif; max-width:660px; padding:0&quot;&gt;&#10;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height:1.6; padding:0&quot;&gt;Europe &amp;middot; 12 weeks &amp;middot; July 20, 2026 &amp;middot; Temporary contract&lt;/div&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;hr /&gt;&#10;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height:1.6; padding:0&quot;&gt;We are looking for an experienced Chief Mate to join a Ro-Ro vessel on European routes. The contract is temporary with a duration of 12 weeks, starting July 20, 2026. Candidates must have relevant experience on Ro-Ro vessels and hold valid &lt;span class=&quot;caps&quot;&gt;STCW&lt;/span&gt; certificates.&lt;/div&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height:1.6; padding:0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height:1.6; padding:0&quot;&gt;- Navigation and watchkeeping duties&lt;br /&gt;&#10; &amp;#8211; Cargo operations and loading/discharging supervision&lt;br /&gt;&#10; &amp;#8211; Deck crew management and safety drills&lt;br /&gt;&#10; &amp;#8211; Ensuring compliance with safety regulations&lt;/div&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height:1.6; padding:0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Essential requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height:1.6; padding:0&quot;&gt;- Valid Chief Mate &lt;span class=&quot;caps&quot;&gt;COC&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&#10; &amp;#8211; Minimum 2 years experience in rank on Ro-Ro vessels&lt;br /&gt;&#10; &amp;#8211; Good command of English&lt;br /&gt;&#10; &amp;#8211; All valid &lt;span class=&quot;caps&quot;&gt;STCW&lt;/span&gt; certificates and medical&lt;/div&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height:1.6; padding:0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#10;&#10;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height:1.6; padding:0&quot;&gt;- Competitive day rates&lt;br /&gt;&#10; &amp;#8211; 12-week contract with possible extension&lt;br /&gt;&#10; &amp;#8211; Professional working environment&lt;/div&gt;&#10;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://maritime-union.com/job/223017/&quot;&gt;Apply to this job&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;</description>
  <link>https://maritime-union.com/job/223017/</link>
  <title>[AI Job] A Chief Mate position is available on a Ro-Ro vessel operating in Europe at ORCA Crew Services</title>
