ates on new vacancies&lt;/div&gt;&#10;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://maritime-union.com/job/223012/&quot;&gt;Apply to this job&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;</description>
